- User interactions include both cart and wishlist engagements, with an increased interaction level for wishlist items; 
- The query integrates user information with detailed recording data and promotion specifics, but only outputs user IDs; 
- The purpose seems to be an analysis of user engagement patterns with audio recordings.

sql:
SELECT recording_id, quantity
FROM cart
WHERE user_id = 1 AND is_saved_for_later = 0;

SELECT title
FROM audio_recordings
WHERE recording_id IN (SELECT recording_id FROM reviews);
